{"tid":92911,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"[極醜惡] 一人N個你見過最柒既街頭音樂？","createTime":"2017-01-24T03:20:31.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-31T09:57:48.000Z","uid":12787,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1377ef6e4dc3afd8838967c42a7149995a960f73","tid":92911,"uid":12787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T03:20:31.000Z","msg":"是咁的，近幾年都多左好多巴打絲打玩街頭音樂。但隨著樣野開始發展蓬勃，就開始出現一堆害群之馬啦。譬如話基本chord都未撚按得實既自稱結他手啦，錯key甩撚曬Beat走撚曬音既Vocal仲有係度鳩拍輕重拍都唔識既cajon手。 例子如下.....<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/fM6CuS\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfM6CuS&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=9c5fd02c\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/fM6CuS</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/hlynMR\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FhlynMR&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=39ef1650\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/hlynMR</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/OEq0nf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FOEq0nf&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=49fda818\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/OEq0nf</a><br />\n<br />\nand more&hellip;..<br />\n<br />\n咁個重點係 呢班人好聲好氣同佢講佢地係唔撚柒聽，而會係覺得人地串佢係嚟踩佢場。我地擔心既地方係唔希望其他人見到呢班垃圾就會一錄鳩打一船人覺得所有香港既真. busker 係咁撚垃圾。 所以我地成立左個facebook page 同 IG page。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6363J08.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6363J08.jpg&h=07049bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/24/110308_5cf8f7b4d2e819fa810327d9d9c52256.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F110308_5cf8f7b4d2e819fa810327d9d9c52256.jpg&h=bacffe11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 希望大家都可以留意下 幫手化身成為fucker 拍低一堆唔撚知出嚟做乜柒係度自娛死撐自己無問題既「busker」並投稿比我地。就用大家既聲音話俾佢地聽佢地既問題係邊度。希望大家支持。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nFB Page ： <a href=\"https://goo.gl/GfpVid\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FGfpVid&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=3703cb8e\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/GfpVid</a><br />\n<br />\nInstagram : <a href=\"https://goo.gl/fZufKi\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FfZufKi&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=e31391a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/fZufKi</a><br />\n<br />\n另外都可以 add 我呢個 ac : <a href=\"https://goo.gl/SGgsd2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FSGgsd2&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=1c738218\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/SGgsd2</a><br />\n<br />\n投稿方法：<br />\n1. IG direct<br />\n2.<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/hhToaHZH37qqDoeA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FhhToaHZH37qqDoeA&d=OessR97wZcg0TsqPXAmbnJkBtgkcD0hE3Em2wkgk6m8%3D&h=c033f611\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/hhToaHZH37qqDoeA</a><br />\n3. 係呢個post留言都得（不過記得比片既link我）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3076bdd3a544d30159d7b74dd6aea0fb1c1040fb","tid":92911,"uid":60074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T03:29:57.000Z","msg":"留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早想屌柒班mk好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"760b61896cd36c16a5a2aa1c75cbc633db2dfa88","tid":92911,"uid":21278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T03:30:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一早想屌柒班mk好耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.g